 and charleston communities of south carolina the bank is an independent community bank concentrating on individuals and small to medium sized businesses its products and services include personal and business checking accounts money market accounts certificates of deposit wire transfers personal savings accounts personal lines of credit personal and commercial loans mortgages safe deposit boxes and credit cards bank of south carolina is based in charleston sc and has branch locations in summerville and mt pleasant sc report you might also consider ad wall  associates  miles away from bank of south carolina wall  associates inc provides personalized attention to the details of each case representing our clients in all dealings with the irs including responding to irs communications on your behalf and pursuing procedural… read more in debt relief services tax services financial advising ad grow financial federal credit union  wescott  miles away from bank of south carolina grow financial is all about more more options more convenience more service more locations at grow financial we want to give more to our members thats why we offer a number of different accounts to choose from atms… read more in banks  credit unions hours mon  am   pm tue  am   pm wed  am   pm thu  am   pm fri  am   pm sat closed sun closed edit business info upcoming special hours mon  closed mon  closed thu  closed mon  closed show more more business info has atm yes business listing provided by ryan h first to review you might also consider ad allstate insurance agent patrick brown  miles as a personal financial representative in charleston i know many local… read more ad allstate insurance agent w phil bradley  miles as a personal financial representative in charleston i know many local… read more other banks  credit unions nearby find more banks  credit unions near bank of south carolina browse nearby restaurants nightlife shopping show all rating details  stars   stars   stars   stars   star 